<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Order PDF</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 11px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #2874a6;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: auto;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        .company-details h1 {
            color: #c0392b;
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .company-details p {
            margin: 2px 0;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .header-right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .header-right h2 {
            color: #2874a6;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .header-right p {
            margin: 3px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .bill-to {
            background-color: #f8f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .bill-to h3 {
            color: #2874a6;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .bill-to h4 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .bill-to p {
            margin: 2px 0;
        }

        .remarks {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #2874a6;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        td {
            font-size: 11px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .product-image {
            max-width: 50px;
            max-height: 50px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .totals-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .totals-table {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .totals-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .totals-table td:first-child {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .total-amount-row {
            background-color: #f8f9f9;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2874a6;
        }

        .terms {
            font-size: 9px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .terms h4 {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .terms ol {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .terms li {
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer-line {
            width: 150px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 5px;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .footer-info {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9f9;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        .amount-words {
            color: #2874a6;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: left !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-left">
            <% if (logo) { %>
                <img src="<%= logo %>" class="logo" alt="Logo">
                <% } %>
                    <div class="company-details">
                        <h1>Kannan Silks</h1>
                        <p>Pure Silk Saree Manufacturer</p>
                        <p>No.2/40, Raja Veethi Road, Chinthamaniyur,</p>
                        <p>Omalur (Via), Salem (Dt.) Pin - 636 455.</p>
                        <p><strong>GSTIN:</strong> 33ABFFK2782B1ZN</p>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> kannansilkshandloom@gmail.com</p>
                        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 63839 00539 / 97877 38094</p>
                    </div>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
            <h2>REQUIREMENT ORDER</h2>
            <p>Order No: <%= order.po_number %>
            </p>
            <p>Date: <%= new Date(order.created_at).toLocaleDateString('en-IN') %>
            </p>
            <p>Transport: <%= order.transporter ? order.transporter.name : 'N/A' %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bill-to">
        <h3>BILL TO (BUYER):</h3>
        <% if (order.buyer) { %>
            <h4>
                <%= order.buyer.first_name %>
                    <%= order.buyer.last_name %>
            </h4>
            <% if (order.buyer.phone) { %>
                <p><strong>Mobile:</strong>
                    <%= order.buyer.phone %>
                </p>
                <% } %>
                    <% if (order.buyer.email) { %>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong>
                            <%= order.buyer.email %>
                        </p>
                        <% } %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <h4>Admin</h4>
                                <% } %>
                                    <% if (order.order_given_by) { %>
                                        <p><strong>Order Given By:</strong>
                                            <%= order.order_given_by %>
                                                <%= order.phone_number ? `(Ph: ${order.phone_number})` : '' %>
                                        </p>
                                        <% } %>
    </div>

    <% if (order.remarks) { %>
        <div class="remarks">
            Remarks: <span style="font-weight: normal;">
                <%= order.remarks %>
            </span>
        </div>
        <% } %>

            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>#</th>
                        <th>Item Code</th>
                        <th>Item Name</th>
                        <th>Color</th>
                        <th>Rate (Rs)</th>
                        <th>Qty</th>
                        <th>Total (Rs)</th>
                        <th>Image</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% order.items.forEach(function(item, index) { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <%= index + 1 %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <%= item.product.product_code %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <%= item.product.name %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <% let color='N/A' ; let imgUrl=null; if (item.variant_id && item.product.images) {
                                    const v=item.product.images.find(img=> img.id === item.variant_id);
                                    if (v) {
                                    color = v.color || 'N/A';
                                    imgUrl = v.base64 || v.url;
                                    }
                                    }
                                    if (color === 'N/A' && item.product.images && item.product.images.length > 0) {
                                    const v = item.product.images[0];
                                    color = v.color || 'N/A';
                                    if (!imgUrl) imgUrl = v.base64 || v.url;
                                    }
                                    %>
                                    <%= color %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <%= parseFloat(item.rate).toFixed(2) %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <%= item.quantity %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <%= parseFloat(item.amount).toFixed(2) %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <% if (imgUrl) { %>
                                    <img src="<%= imgUrl %>" class="product-image" alt="Product Image">
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        -
                                        <% } %>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <% }); %>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <table class="totals-table">
                <% 
                const totalQty = order.items.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.quantity, 0);
                const subtotal = parseFloat(order.total_amount);
                
                let totalGstAmount = 0;
                order.items.forEach(item => {
                    const itemAmount = parseFloat(item.amount);
                    const taxPercent = parseFloat(item.tax_percent || (item.product && item.product.gst) || 0);
                    const itemGst = itemAmount * (taxPercent / 100);
                    totalGstAmount += itemGst;
                });
                
                const grandTotal = subtotal + totalGstAmount;
                
                // Find unique non-zero GST rates
                const uniqueGstRates = [...new Set(order.items.map(item => parseFloat(item.tax_percent || (item.product && item.product.gst) || 0)))].filter(rate => rate > 0);
                const gstLabel = uniqueGstRates.length > 0 ? `GST : ${uniqueGstRates.join(', ')} %` : 'GST : 0 %';
                %>
                <tr>
                        <td>Total Quantity: <%= totalQty %>
                        </td>
                        <td>Total Amount (Without GST): Rs. <%= subtotal.toFixed(2) %>
                        </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= gstLabel %></td>
                    <td>GST VALUE : Rs. <%= totalGstAmount.toFixed(2) %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="total-amount-row">
                    <td class="amount-words">Amount in Words: <%= amountInWords(grandTotal) %> Only</td>
                    <td>Grand Total: Rs. <%= grandTotal.toFixed(2) %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <div class="terms">
                <h4>Terms & Conditions</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Order Confirmation:</strong> All orders are subject to acceptance and confirmation by
                        the seller.</li>
                    <li><strong>Price Validity:</strong> Prices displayed on the portal are wholesale prices and may
                        change without prior notice.</li>
                    <li><strong>Credit Facility and payment terms:</strong> Credit payment is available only to approved
                        buyers. Credit limits and payment periods are decided by the seller.</li>
                    <li><strong>Credit Payment Due Date:</strong> Buyers must make payment within the agreed credit
                        period. Delayed payments may result in suspension of further orders.</li>
                    <li><strong>Late Payment Charges:</strong> The seller reserves the right to charge 18% interest or
                        late fees on overdue payments as permitted by applicable law.</li>
                    <li><strong>Product Availability:</strong> All products are subject to stock availability. If an
                        item is unavailable, the buyer will be informed accordingly.</li>
                    <li><strong>Returns and Claims:</strong> Returns are accepted only for damaged, defective, or
                        wrongly supplied products. Claims must be raised within 15 days of delivery with supporting
                        photos.</li>
                    <li><strong>Shipping and Delivery:</strong> Delivery dates are estimates only. The seller is not
                        responsible for delays caused by transporters, couriers, or unforeseen circumstances.</li>
                    <li><strong>Ownership of Goods:</strong> Goods supplied on credit remain the property of the seller
                        until full payment is received. The seller reserves the right to recover goods in case of
                        payment default.</li>
                </ol>
                <p>Declaration: By placing an order through the portal, the buyer confirms that they have read,
                    understood, and agreed to these Terms & Conditions.</p>
            </div>

            <div
                style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 40px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px;">
                <div>Delivery Date: _________________</div>
                <div>For KANNAN SILKS</div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-line">Buyer Signature</div>
                <div class="footer-line">Authorised Signatory</div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-info">
                Reg Office: No.2/40, Raja Veethi Road, Chinthamaniyur, Omalur (Via), Salem (Dt.) Pin - 636 455. |
                E-Mail: kannansilkshandloom@gmail.com | Phone: 63839 00539 / 97877 38094
            </div>

</body>

</html>